### Set up your text editor

Because Chef uses _code_ to express infrastructure policy, it's important that you use a text editor that provides features such as syntax highlighting and line numbering.

Install a text editor now. [Atom](http://atom.io) and [Sublime Text](http://www.sublimetext.com) are popular text editors for graphical user environments. If you prefer the command line, `emacs`, `nano`, and `vim` are popular.

